{"word":"ἐγχάσκω","slug":"ἐγχάσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐγχάσκω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-χανοῦμαι</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>ἐγχανεῖν</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>as if from *<el>ἐγχαίνω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to gape</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to grin</i> or <i>scoff at</i> one, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}